== 製作 ==
該片在2013年9月14日於[[美國|美國]][[新奧爾良|新奧爾良]]進行拍攝，其後在2013年11月19日，轉在[[布宜诺斯艾利斯|布宜诺斯艾利斯]]拍攝為期3星期。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Fresh Prince of Polo: A casual Will Smith hangs out with Argentine model during break from filming new movie Focus|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2509215/Will-Smith-hangs-Argentine-model-polo.html|accessdate=2013-11-18|newspaper=Mail Online|date=2013-11-18|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222625/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2509215/Will-Smith-hangs-Argentine-model-polo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後拍攝於[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]為12月10日。<ref>{{cite news|title=Will Smith & Margot Robbie Keep Their Distance On Their Last Day Of Shooting In Argentina|url=http://perezhilton.com/2013-12-10-will-smith-margot-robbie-focus-movie-set-last-day-filming|accessdate=2013-12-10|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007001852/https://perezhilton.com/2013-12-10-will-smith-margot-robbie-focus-movie-set-last-day-filming/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年12月17日於[[紐約市|紐約市]]進行殺青。<ref>{{cite news|title=Will Smith and Margot Robbie Wrap "Focus"|url=http://www.whosay.com/articles/506-will-smith-and-margot-robbie-wrap-focus/|accessdate=2013-12-17|archive-date=2016-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801004832/http://www.whosay.com/articles/506-will-smith-and-margot-robbie-wrap-focus/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

